blog.name: swiftiesgonnashakeitoff
blog.title: GINA 💗
blog.description:
| 17 🦋 | Germany 🇩🇪

REP Tour London Night 1 - first time seeing Taylor ✨

I love cats, dancing, baking and riding my bike, but most of all I love Taylor! You made my life so so much better. 💗

Met my best friend @picturesinfrxmes because of you 💗

summary: Another thing that I remember so clearly from London Night 1. Before the show started we were like exploring London and we went...
body:
Another thing that I remember so clearly from London Night 1. Before the show started we were like exploring London and we went back to our apartment at like 3PM or something to get ready, so I got changed, put my costume on and got a text from Myrthe that she and her mom are leaving now for Wembley. I texted back that we would leave the house in a few minutes to get there.

So we did that and walked to the underground station (to anyone who lives in London: it was Stockwell Station and it took us about 45 minutes to get to Wembley) so I was walking the streets of London in my costume and we got off the train at Kings Cross Station and let me tell you there were SO MANY PEOPLE. It literally was insane, every single one of them wanted to get to Wembley and there were so many girls in a costume or a fan shirt and they all smiled at me and I was so happy like I have never seen so many Taylor Fans at one place (I am literally the only one in my school) and it was so nice of them to smile at me and tell me that my outfit looked nice 😭 (I LOVE YOU GUYS💗)

So we had to wait for a second underground train, because the first one was full. So we got into the second train with like 1000 other people and went to Wembley. I got a text from Myrth telling me that they already got there and that they are waiting for us and I got sooo nervous because I didn’t want to be late!!!

(to be continued) @picturesinfrxmes

me on the way to the underground station + my dad, sister and I in the underground (we all looked pretty bad so I put the hearts on our faces hahaha) + my chat with Myrthe before leaving for the show jxjyjyj
